 <arm>
   <uof name="Swept_Solid">
     <description>
The Topologically_Bounded_Surface UoF specifies the data structure for the description of solids created by sweeping a bounded planar face. 
The face may be either linearly extruded or revolved to create the solid. The face is required to be planar and to conform to the specification of an advanced face.
with fully defined geometry and explicit topology defining the boundaries. 
Edges are required to have their geometry defined by curves.
     </description>
     <uof.ae entity="Swept_solid"/>
   </uof>

